Text: FW NDAHi Tana I was told to pass this NDA info below to you Would you please email this to Vince Cook at his email address noted below with a cc to me Please let me know if you have any questions Thank you Nick Original Message From Cook Vincent mailto Sent Thursday October PM To Tubach Nick Subject RE NDA Nick Assume you will send a soft copy so I can forward to legal for review Thanks Vince COMSYS Information Technology Services Inc Post Oak Parkway Suite Houston TX Contact Vincent E Cook Senior Vice President General Manager West Division Original Message From Tubach Nick mailto Sent Thursday October PM To Cook Vincent Subject NDA Hi Vince It was good to talk to you today I need the following for the NDA Exact legal name Corp Address Contact if other than you and title Hopefully we can strike a mutually fruitful relationship Talk to you soon Nick PS Also just a couple of suggestions for your web site team Get rid of the boing mouseovers on the main pageThats awful Under Contact it should be more than a form to email in Add contact information Just my thoughts I liked your previous site from a userfriendliness perspective better This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you
